snippet.title: JUMP FORCE - Calling All Heroes Launch Trailer Remix | XB1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Now it's YOUR TURN to show the world what type of hero you are in JUMP FORCE! Unite to Fight offline & online with your personal avatars or choose from 40 Shonen Jump heroes and villains.  

#JUMPFORCE is now on X1, PS4, and PC. Order your copy today:  https://bandainam.co/JumpForcePO

#UniteToFight #BandaiNamco
